[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":2264},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fgit\u002F20221115\u002F721294310\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fgit\u002F20221115\u002F721294310\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fgit\u002F20221115\u002F721294310\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fgit\u002F20221115\u002F721294310\u002F":2240,"related:\u002Fgit\u002F20221115\u002F721294310\u002F":2249},"\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002F2022\u002F11\u002F15\u002Fprettier-git-commit-with-git-cz\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":2224,"date":2225,"description":18,"extension":2226,"lang":2227,"meta":2228,"navigation":2229,"path":2230,"readingMinutes":2231,"seo":2232,"standalone":2233,"stem":2234,"tags":2235,"tldr":2237,"updated":2225,"url":2238,"__hash__":2239},"content\u002FGit\u002F來吧！讓你的-git-cz-Git-Commit-訊息更美一點！.md","來吧！用 git-cz 讓你的 Git Commit 訊息更美一點！","721294310",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":2212},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,37,40,65,68,75,78,81,84,92,98,106,109,114,117,146,149,153,156,169,172,194,205,210,213,219,226,231,238,243,250,256,262,265,276,279,287,290,294,297,304,1035,1038,1597,1600,1606,1610,1613,1616,1619,2159,2162,2166,2169,2185,2191,2198,2201,2208],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"你有想過嗎？你的 Git Commit 是不是有點醜呢？然後時常不知道到底要寫什麼？如果有的話，那麼這一篇就要來介紹一個工具，也就是 git-cz，讓你解放你的 Git Commit 訊息，讓你的 Git Commit 更美更漂亮，說是懶人福音也不為過唷。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"git-commit-的重要性","Git Commit 的重要性",[16,24,25,26,31,32,36],{},"一開始我們先聊一下 Git Commit 的重要性，在以前我有分享過一篇文章叫做「",[27,28,30],"a",{"href":29},"\u002Fgit\u002F20200914\u002F1124442109\u002F","淺談 Git Flow 與 commit 規範","」，其中裡面有提到關於「",[27,33,35],{"href":34},"\u002Fgit\u002F20200914\u002F1124442109\u002F#Git-Commit-%E8%A6%8F%E7%AF%84","Git Commit 規範","」的部分。",[16,38,39],{},"而這裡面有特別提到 Commit Type 的重要",[41,42,43,47,50,53,56,59,62],"ul",{},[44,45,46],"li",{},"feat - 新增\u002F修改功能 (Feature)",[44,48,49],{},"fix - 修正 Bug (bug fix)",[44,51,52],{},"docs - 修改\u002F新增文件 (documentation)",[44,54,55],{},"style - 修改程式碼格式或風格，不影響原有運作，例如 ESLint (formatting, missing semi colons, …)",[44,57,58],{},"refactor - 重構 or 優化，不屬於 bug 也不屬於新增功能等",[44,60,61],{},"test - 增加測試功能 (when adding missing tests)",[44,63,64],{},"chore - 增加或修改第三方套件(輔助工具)等 (maintain)",[16,66,67],{},"儘管我們已經知道這個概念，但實際開發上可能會忘記每個 Commit Type 的意義，或是不知道該怎麼寫，這時候就會出現一些醜醜的 Commit 訊息，例如...",[16,69,70],{},[71,72],"img",{"alt":73,"src":74},"一推沒意義的 Commit","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FmvvoGyr.png",[16,76,77],{},"上面這張圖是取至於我的部落格，完全一推沒有意義的 Commit，原因是為什麼呢？因為我懶人癌症發作，所以不想多花時間去思考 Commit Type。",[16,79,80],{},"因此為了解決這個問題，我們將要來介紹本篇的主題，也就是 git-cz。",[12,82,83],{"id":83},"git-cz",[16,85,86,91],{},[27,87,83],{"href":88,"rel":89},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fstreamich\u002Fgit-cz",[90],"nofollow"," 是一個 Commit 管理工具，可以讓你的 Commit 統一格式且更美觀，舉例來講：",[16,93,94],{},[71,95],{"alt":96,"src":97},"Image","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FVoqohiU.png",[16,99,100,101,105],{},"上面這張圖是我簡單示範使用 git-cz 的畫面，你可以看到至少比用 ",[102,103,104],"code",{},"post"," 好很多，而且還有漂漂的 Emoji，這樣的 Commit 訊息，不香嗎？",[16,107,108],{},"那麼該怎麼使用呢？本身 git-cz 有提供多種安裝方式(npm or npx)，而這一篇我將會示範使用 npm 安裝，並且是 Global 的方式，其主要原因是或許你會因此愛上 git-cz，所以想要在其他專案也使用，而不是每個專案都要安裝一次。",[110,111,113],"h3",{"id":112},"安裝-git-cz","安裝 git-cz",[16,115,116],{},"首先請打開終端機輸入以下指令",[118,119,124],"pre",{"className":120,"code":121,"language":122,"meta":123,"style":123},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","npm install -g git-cz\n","bash","",[102,125,126],{"__ignoreMap":123},[127,128,131,135,139,143],"span",{"class":129,"line":130},"line",1,[127,132,134],{"class":133},"s_sBn","npm",[127,136,138],{"class":137},"sTRMh"," install",[127,140,142],{"class":141},"sCcAr"," -g",[127,144,145],{"class":137}," git-cz\n",[16,147,148],{},"沒錯！就是這麼簡單，接著我們就可以準備開始使用 git-cz 囉~",[110,150,152],{"id":151},"使用-git-cz","使用 git-cz",[16,154,155],{},"接著請你隨便打開一個專案，並且進入到該專案的資料夾，接著輸入以下指令",[118,157,159],{"className":120,"code":158,"language":122,"meta":123,"style":123},"git cz\n",[102,160,161],{"__ignoreMap":123},[127,162,163,166],{"class":129,"line":130},[127,164,165],{"class":133},"git",[127,167,168],{"class":137}," cz\n",[16,170,171],{},"這時候你應該會噴出一段錯誤訊息",[118,173,175],{"className":120,"code":174,"language":122,"meta":123,"style":123},"✖  error     No files staged!\n",[102,176,177],{"__ignoreMap":123},[127,178,179,182,185,188,191],{"class":129,"line":130},[127,180,181],{"class":133},"✖",[127,183,184],{"class":137},"  error",[127,186,187],{"class":137},"     No",[127,189,190],{"class":137}," files",[127,192,193],{"class":137}," staged!\n",[16,195,196,197,200,201,204],{},"其主要原因是因為你沒有把檔案加入到 Stage(意指 ",[102,198,199],{},"git add .",")，所以 git-cz 會噴出這個錯誤訊息，所以請你先把檔案加入到 Stage，接著再輸入 ",[102,202,203],{},"git cz","，這時候你就會看到 git-cz 的畫面了。",[16,206,207],{},[71,208],{"alt":83,"src":209},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F0nv9riK.png",[16,211,212],{},"你可以透過方向鍵去選取你本次 Commit 的類型，那麼這些 Commit 類型都是 git-cz 所預設提供的（如果你想客製化我後面會再介紹），接著選取你要的 Commit 類型後可以按下 Enter，然後你會看到 git-cz 會叫你填寫一下當前 Commit 的內容，這時候你就可以填寫你的 Commit 訊息了。",[16,214,215],{},[71,216],{"alt":217,"src":218},"輸入 commit 訊息","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fn6hpyff.png",[16,220,221,222,225],{},"輸入完畢後，再按一次 Enter 他會再問你「",[102,223,224],{},"Provide a longer description of the change","」，這句話意思是指更詳細的修改說明，如果沒有要填寫的話，你可以直接按下 Enter 略過",[16,227,228],{},[71,229],{"alt":224,"src":230},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FVumvDYy.png",[16,232,233,234,237],{},"接著你應該會被問 「",[102,235,236],{},"List any breaking changes","」，這句話意思是指是否有破壞性的修改，如果沒有的話，一樣可以直接按下 Enter 略過",[16,239,240],{},[71,241],{"alt":236,"src":242},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FJieVcKJ.png",[16,244,245,246,249],{},"最後一個則是「",[102,247,248],{},"Issues this commit closes, e.g #123","」，這句話意思是指是否有對應的 Issue，如果沒有的話，一樣可以直接按下 Enter 略過，這樣子你的 Commit 就完成了。",[16,251,252],{},[71,253],{"alt":254,"src":255},"完成 Commit","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FsZJXrlo.png",[16,257,258,259,261],{},"透過選取跟問答的方式我們可以輕輕鬆鬆地獲取一個漂亮的 Commit 訊息，而這些規範基本上都與「",[27,260,35],{"href":34},"」觀念相同，因此是完全可以沿用的，但是卻可以讓我們更快速地完成 Commit，而且也不用擔心格式錯誤跟人為的錯誤，因此這個也可以稱之為懶人福音，真正的解放大腦！",[16,263,264],{},"那麼這邊提醒一下，改用 git-cz 之後，你要將你原本輸入指令方式稍微調整一下，例如：",[16,266,267,269,270,269,273],{},[102,268,199],{}," => ",[102,271,272],{},"git commit -m 'first'",[102,274,275],{},"git push",[16,277,278],{},"改成",[16,280,281,269,283,269,285],{},[102,282,199],{},[102,284,203],{},[102,286,275],{},[16,288,289],{},"這樣子才能正確使用 git cz 唷。",[110,291,293],{"id":292},"客製化-git-cz","客製化 git-cz",[16,295,296],{},"如果你覺得 git-cz 預設的 Commit 類型不夠用，你可以透過以下方式來客製化你的 Commit 類型",[16,298,299,300,303],{},"首先打開你的專案，並在專案根目錄下新增一個檔案，檔案名稱為 ",[102,301,302],{},"changelog.config.js","，而這個內容其實官方有提供預設的，這邊我有補上中文註解，讓你可以直接複製貼上方便自己修改",[118,305,309],{"className":306,"code":307,"language":308,"meta":123,"style":123},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","module.exports = {\n  disableEmoji: false, \u002F\u002F 是否禁用 emoji\n  format: '{type}{scope}: {emoji}{subject}', \u002F\u002F Commit 訊息的格式\n  list: ['test', 'feat', 'fix', 'chore', 'docs', 'refactor', 'style', 'ci', 'perf'], \u002F\u002F Commit 類型的清單\n  maxMessageLength: 64, \u002F\u002F Commit 訊息的最大長度\n  minMessageLength: 3, \u002F\u002F Commit 訊息的最小長度\n  questions: ['type', 'scope', 'subject', 'body', 'breaking', 'issues', 'lerna'], \u002F\u002F 問題的清單\n  scopes: [], \u002F\u002F Commit 範圍的清單\n  types: { \u002F\u002F Commit 類型的清單\n    chore: {\n      description: 'Build process or auxiliary tool changes', \u002F\u002F Commit 類型的描述\n      emoji: '🤖', \u002F\u002F Commit 類型的 emoji\n      value: 'chore' \u002F\u002F Commit 類型的值\n    },\n    ci: {\n      description: 'CI related changes',\n      emoji: '🎡',\n      value: 'ci'\n    },\n    docs: {\n      description: 'Documentation only changes',\n      emoji: '✏️',\n      value: 'docs'\n    },\n    feat: {\n      description: 'A new feature',\n      emoji: '🎸',\n      value: 'feat'\n    },\n    fix: {\n      description: 'A bug fix',\n      emoji: '🐛',\n      value: 'fix'\n    },\n    perf: {\n      description: 'A code change that improves performance',\n      emoji: '⚡️',\n      value: 'perf'\n    },\n    refactor: {\n      description: 'A code change that neither fixes a bug or adds a feature',\n      emoji: '💡',\n      value: 'refactor'\n    },\n    release: {\n      description: 'Create a release commit',\n      emoji: '🏹',\n      value: 'release'\n    },\n    style: {\n      description: 'Markup, white-space, formatting, missing semi-colons...',\n      emoji: '💄',\n      value: 'style'\n    },\n    test: {\n      description: 'Adding missing tests',\n      emoji: '💍',\n      value: 'test'\n    },\n  },\n  messages: {  \u002F\u002F Commit 的訊息描述\n    type: 'Select the type of change that you\\'re committing:',\n    customScope: 'Select the scope this component affects:',\n    subject: 'Write a short, imperative mood description of the change:\\n',\n    body: 'Provide a longer description of the change:\\n ',\n    breaking: 'List any breaking changes:\\n',\n    footer: 'Issues this commit closes, e.g #123:',\n    confirmCommit: 'The packages that this commit has affected\\n',\n  },\n};\n","js",[102,310,311,330,346,360,415,429,443,487,496,504,510,524,538,549,555,561,572,582,590,595,601,611,621,629,634,640,650,660,668,673,679,689,699,707,712,718,728,738,746,751,757,767,777,785,790,796,806,816,824,829,835,845,855,863,868,874,884,894,902,907,913,922,939,950,967,983,998,1009,1024,1029],{"__ignoreMap":123},[127,312,313,316,320,323,327],{"class":129,"line":130},[127,314,315],{"class":141},"module",[127,317,319],{"class":318},"sMAXC",".",[127,321,322],{"class":141},"exports",[127,324,326],{"class":325},"sWyjQ"," =",[127,328,329],{"class":318}," {\n",[127,331,333,336,339,342],{"class":129,"line":332},2,[127,334,335],{"class":318},"  disableEmoji: ",[127,337,338],{"class":141},"false",[127,340,341],{"class":318},", ",[127,343,345],{"class":344},"sQrFR","\u002F\u002F 是否禁用 emoji\n",[127,347,349,352,355,357],{"class":129,"line":348},3,[127,350,351],{"class":318},"  format: ",[127,353,354],{"class":137},"'{type}{scope}: {emoji}{subject}'",[127,356,341],{"class":318},[127,358,359],{"class":344},"\u002F\u002F C